    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The remaining 6 factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 assessment plan. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The assessment team accepts this model for the stated decision-making purpose. Note: this record is filed under the Minimal profile; a full structured Context of Use declaration was not included in this submission.",
